query:
SELECT 
                COALESCE(url, '') as "url!",
                COALESCE(ip, '') as "ip!",
                COALESCE(isp, '') as "isp!",
                COALESCE(country, '') as "country!",
                latency as "latency!",
                COALESCE(code, '') as "code!"
            FROM proxies 
            WHERE latency > 0 AND latency < $1 AND latency IS NOT NULL
            AND url IS NOT NULL 
            AND ip IS NOT NULL 
            AND code = $2
            ORDER BY latency ASC
            LIMIT 1
